{"tid":1604442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城 Online] 改正陋習，救自己一命","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T03:45:59.000Z","uid":236171,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8358321d023cfdac7094ffa9c8908ac01290b147","tid":1604442,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打香城 Online見到好多送頭陋習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口臭都要再提</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 唔好孭有手柄/露出繩索嘅背囊</span></strong><br />\n~~~<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKpXLZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKpXLZP.jpg&h=3601ddac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 有繩一係加 rain cover，一係剪</span></strong><br />\n~~~(rain cover 仲可以防止被狗認到背囊）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 背囊千祈<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>孭前面</span></strong><br />\n~~~咁樣兩條孭帶會去咗後面，仲易捉<br />\n~~~捉住咗你仲要除唔到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 冇用 rain cover 嘅帶個後備索袋</span></strong><br />\n~~~換裝嘅時候成個背囊塞入去<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5. 長頭髮手足唔該扎髻收入帽</span></strong><br />\n~~~<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gVzOc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gVzOc0.jpg&h=2cdfaf6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6. 方便換裝，黑風褸雜色 T-Shirt</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n仲有咩要注意，歡迎再加<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n武運昌隆"},{"pid":"70a39014dc746fc46b720037f055367b47c5d350","tid":1604442,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:20:52.000Z","msg":"十一賀佢老母"},{"pid":"576a20d884f023db562963caea6c87b9319275f9","tid":1604442,"uid":219583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:20:59.000Z","m